      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m a postdoctoral researcher in the Data Science Institute at Columbia University, working with &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cs.columbia.edu/~blei/&#34;&gt; David Blei. &lt;/a&gt; My work focuses on applied causality. Broadly, I adapt modern ML and NLP methods for causal inference, especially from text data. I focus on applications to social science and algorithmic fairness.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I received my PhD from University of California Santa Cruz, where I worked with &lt;a href=&#34;https://getoor.soe.ucsc.edu&#34;&gt; Lise Getoor. &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
